  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onions and cook until they are lightly browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic and ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the goat meat and cook until it is browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the cumin, coriander, cinnamon, turmeric, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper. Stir to combine.",
    "Add the beef broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, until the meat is tender, about 1 1/2 hours.",
    "Serve the tagine hot, garnished with fresh parsley or cilantro if desired.",
    "Ensure poultry is cooked to an internal temperature of 74°C / 165°F (juices run clear, no pink remaining) before serving."
  ],
